Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:04.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我受不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:05.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不想再複習考試了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:07.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們去遊戲廳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:10.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然你這麼說 那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:12.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:15.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,光學習的話腦子會變笨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:17.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我還要複習…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:19.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:21.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:24.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去玩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:29.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 下一次考試我必須得考一個好成績
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:36.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 我可以坐這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:42.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是在做考前複習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:44.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——op———
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:28.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,考前複習
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:32.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剛才我碰見高尾他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:36.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剛才我們還在一起複習
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:42.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,他們很興奮地喊著「去玩啦」 然後衝出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片不和他們一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可沒時間去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:51.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是這次的考試沒有考到年級前五十的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:54.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的遊戲就會被沒收
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:58.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:04.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,糟了 我為什麼要說個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:08.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是告訴她了 她肯定會來妨礙我學習的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,開…開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:19.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:22.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總之 不要打擾我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:26.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真過分 說得我好像總是打擾你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:27.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:29.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,捉弄西片很有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,換個地方自習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:39.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過那麼做的話 就好像輸給了高木同學似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:45.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學不複習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:49.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 我一天只學兩個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:56.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不愧是高木同學 年級前十真從容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:00.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 她到底在打什麼算盤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:05.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她可是高木同學 肯定想著要怎麼搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她不可能會乖乖待著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:08.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為她可是高木同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:12.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:15.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,與其說沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:18.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不如說光是看著就…其實也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:18.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那裡 錯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:19.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:24.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,第六問 求-2+3y分之x的值那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:26.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 這裡錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:27.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:29.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪裡錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:36.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個是…我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,坐這邊比較好教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:54.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我看看 x=-16 y=-1 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:56.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學竟然要教我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}首先這樣代入進去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她究竟在打什麼算盤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你把式子列出來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:02.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:05.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後 因為這裡是負數乘以負數
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以要注意計算的順序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:09.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 答案是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:11.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 正確
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這裡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:18.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學真厲害啊 僅僅瞅了一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:22.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 我不是很懂這部分的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我從頭開始教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學真可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:34.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 這也太可疑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:38.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼她會這麼親切啊 太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:43.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 你為什麼今天會這麼親切啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:45.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:50.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 就是覺得你今天真溫柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:57.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個嘛 因為我在上課時總是在捉弄西片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:00.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,如果你成績下降了的話我會愧疚的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,平時那樣對你 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:08.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這次努力考一個好成績吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:17.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你終於改過自新了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你請我喝果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:29.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天託高木同學的福 感覺數學進步很大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:33.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣一來就不用擔心遊戲被沒收了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:38.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其實高木同學說不定是個好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:42.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天真的很謝謝你了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不用客氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為今天我教你的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在考試範圍外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:58.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你已經搞明白代入法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:02.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然我弄明白了 快把果汁還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 我已經打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:04.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是剛剛打開的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,考試
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:10.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把試卷交上來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:16.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺不錯 肯定能拿到九十分以上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:17.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不錯不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:21.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這裡教教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:24.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不擅長英語
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:27.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 說得好像你擅長其他科目一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的意思是最不擅長這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以 關於這裡的翻譯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:38.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我想自己複習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 明明你平時都願意教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是這次考試 每一科都拿到九十分以上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我爸媽就給我買想要的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:52.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這裡要怎麼翻譯成否定句呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:53.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:56.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總之我現在沒空教你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:57.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:01.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,遊戲和朋友哪邊更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:03.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:06.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然你可以玩遊戲 但你能教功課的只有朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:07.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:14.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,礙事的傢伙都不在了 趁現在再看一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 發卷子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,傳到後面去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:22.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 考試前的複習也很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:26.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這次英語考試一定也能考到九十分以上…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,數學？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,發卷子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:35.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你有認真在學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,下一個 齋藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼一副不安的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:46.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這次也做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木你考了多少分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,待會一起看下分數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:08:59.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,考得不錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過不是一百分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真不愧是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:09.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,下一個 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你再加把勁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,考得不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:23.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說的好像事不關己似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:25.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你自己複習好了就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:28.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,卻把範圍外的考點教得這麼詳細
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們來猜對方的分數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:35.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最接近的一方為勝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:37.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼總是那麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:42.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯…五十分左右？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你太小瞧我了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:50.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那 是高於六十分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來是低於六十分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼她會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:10:01.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,撲克臉 要用撲克臉來混淆她的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高於五十五分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看來沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以要在五十五到五十九之間選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:15.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,決不能讓她猜到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,五十六？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:23.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,五十七
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,五十八
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:28.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,五十九
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是五十六分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:37.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那樣就行了嗎 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:42.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的考試成績是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:45.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,五十九分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:49.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,猜錯了 真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惜的是你的分數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,您說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,差了三分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:06.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那輪到你猜我的分數了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誤差在兩分以內的話 西片就贏了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:13.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 讓我來看穿高木同學的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:18.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被老師表揚了 就說明是九十分以上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:22.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼是九十二分左右？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個反應是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:28.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高於九十五分？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,九十分左右？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,九十二？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:43.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她一定在撒謊 怎能被她給騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:46.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學不可能會露出那樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 她在戲弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:50.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我要全力以赴 贏下這場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:54.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再集中一些 看清楚她的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:57.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:01.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是從剛才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:06.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們倆一直相互注視著而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要轉過去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太卑鄙了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:16.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你這麼一說 我豈不是不能看你的表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:21.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,動動腦子想一想 有沒有什麼提示…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:24.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,表情假得一眼就能看穿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:28.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這說明高木同學想讓我以為她考了九十二分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:33.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也就是說 誤差在兩分以內的九十到九十四之間是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:37.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再者 被老師表揚了意味著考了九十分以上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:40.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且還不是一百分 也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:44.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是九十五分到九十九分之間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:47.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,完美 完美地贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:51.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學的成績是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,九十七分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:59.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真可惜 是九十二分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:01.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你太多疑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:07.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還故意讓了你 猜錯三分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:10.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:22.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,書店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰都不要過來 誰都不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:41.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一共420元…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:44.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:44.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,您需要書皮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:45.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:46.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,袋子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:48.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,小票…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:49.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:51.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,買到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:54.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接下來只要回家慢慢享受就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:01.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學？為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我是來散步的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道她讀懂了我的想法？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:09.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,糟了 要是讓她看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這裡無論如何都要糊弄過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:14.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 我有本想買的書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惜都賣光了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:19.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 說不定我在收銀台的時候被她看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:23.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我買了「爆裂最強足球」的第十一卷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:26.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這本書雖然在男生之間很流行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:28.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但女生肯定沒興趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是完美的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:32.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我真聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,爆裂足球？讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:35.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:38.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我還沒看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:40.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讓我看看封面也好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行不行 絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:44.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也還沒好好看過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我們一起看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:47.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我喜歡一個人看…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒想到她會如此窮追猛打 真是個危險的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還是快點離開她為上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:57.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那再見了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:05.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:08.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難得遇到了 一起走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:11.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:16.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大清早的在這麼遠的書店遇見你可是非常少見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:23.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一想到背包裡還裝著絕對不能被她看見的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我心裡就不踏實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:27.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好想快點回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:30.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:33.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是不是對我撒謊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你撒謊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:40.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你買的不是爆裂足球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不惜撒謊還要藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定是買了什麼羞羞的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:51.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是普通的少女漫畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:54.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「百分百單相思」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:57.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 雖然是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:59.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你為什麼會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:03.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我偶然路過的時候看到了在收銀台前的西片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:05.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後瞅到了標題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:08.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明知是這樣還要來戲弄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是因為動畫很有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:12.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來你也會看這種書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:16.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這件事可以不要告訴其他人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,先不說電視上的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:20.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是讓人知道我連單行本都買的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:22.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定會被大家嘲笑我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要怎麼辦呢 你剛才還對我撒謊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:30.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我對西片可是一次謊也沒撒過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:34.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我知道了 我不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這麼乾脆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:38.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的真的不要告訴別人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:45.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎 感覺你的回答好敷衍哦 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你真煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:55.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我把自己的秘密告訴西片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:57.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是相互知道對方的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你也會放心一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:02.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:05.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你把耳朵湊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:11.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我喜歡西片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:17.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:20.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼？高木同學？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:24.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你臉紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:25.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片你真是容易臉紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:29.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為西片對我撒謊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:32.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以作為報復 我也要對你撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來是騙人的嗎 嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:38.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 騙你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:40.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定是騙你的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:44.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再見啦 我走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:45.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,拜拜 再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:51.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,騙我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:58.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也想看百分百單相思 下次借給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:04.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,聲音太大啦 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,避雨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:12.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,突然就下起雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不知要下多久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:18.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:22.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,連襪子也濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:25.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片沒濕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:28.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的衣服都濕透了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:30.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:33.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,平常心 平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是她發現了我在動搖的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,毫無疑問會被她認定為色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是雨能早點停就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:43.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還想早點回去呢 五點過後有我想看的動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:45.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,當然 是爆裂足球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是之前你在書店買的那本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:52.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 不對 那是百分百單相思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:54.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是約好了不說這事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:57.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和西片說沒關係吧 畢竟是本人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:02.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是雨能早點停就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:05.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:12.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 有點濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說西片 你帶了運動服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以借給我嗎 我會洗乾淨再還給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:20.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想換一下衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,換衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,換我的運動服？在這兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:27.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 我的衣服濕噠噠的穿著難受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:29.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:32.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且 西片的眼睛也不知道該往哪兒擱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被她發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把臉轉過去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:37.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:40.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片沒怎麼被淋濕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:42.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:43.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:45.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你用傘來遮雨了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:51.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 我推著自行車不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:53.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:57.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,想看的話可以轉過來看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:01.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 你在說什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:03.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我已經換完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:06.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你慌什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:09.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又被她耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:12.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 我們來打個賭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:17.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,賭五點的校鈴響前 雨能不能停
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:19.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,輸的一方要聽從勝者的任何要求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:20.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片選哪邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我賭雨不能停
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我就賭雨能停
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雨要是能停 我就能回家看爆裂足球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:33.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是不能停 也能命令高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,無論結果如何 我都有賺頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:39.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過換了衣服之後還真是舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:42.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是有點汗臭味兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為是夏天 這種事情是肯定的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:53.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接觸過我身體的布料正緊貼著高木同學的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:56.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不可以 我在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:58.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 是貓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:58.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是來避雨的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:02.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:04.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然它很可愛 但你要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:05.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這傢伙會撓人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:10.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要把運動服還給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,穿我的運動服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:17.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:20.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然有點濕 但總比你身上的要好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:27.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我要穿上這塊和高木同學的身體親密接觸的布料嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你換好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:32.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 不要看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:36.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺自己在做著不能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,味道好香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:54.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:55.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要讓你做什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,隨便了 反正回到家還有爆裂足球看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:03.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,趕緊應付完跑回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:04.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:09.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好不容易轉晴了 回家之前先逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:11.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是高木同學 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:13.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說好了輸的一方無論說什麼都要聽從的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:14.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:17.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Comment: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:50.11,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:54.53,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:01:04.87,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:13.67,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:21.97,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:24.93,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:30.32,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:34.19,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:38.11,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:46.21,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:54.51,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:59.93,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:03.89,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:14.15,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:50.11,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:54.53,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:01:04.87,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:13.67,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校園的庭院 第一個發現你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:21.97,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你說些什麼呢 即便是想著這些也是一種樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:24.93,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗簾隨風起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:30.32,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不經意地投入一束陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:34.19,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美麗的容顏笑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:38.11,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:46.21,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風兒喧囂 似要吹散考試的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:54.51,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}吶 我想要和你一起 立下兩人的秘密約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:59.93,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:03.89,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:14.15,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:36.25,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}プールサイドで　夢を見ていたの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:42.09,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しいほどに　あなたの声が響いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:46.42,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}響いてるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:51.26,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}昨日のあたし　まるで子猫なの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:56.94,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}かすかに分かる　白い毛並みが震えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:23:01.19,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}震えてるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:09.07,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}それが恋をしていた日　あなたを好きな日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:13.03,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ　忘れないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.03,0:23:20.04,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}恋していた　あたしのこと　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:25.00,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}自転車こいで　海を見に行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:28.88,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}夜明けの空に　太陽をめがけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.88,0:23:32.64,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}飾らない日の　おしゃべりは続き
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:40.23,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}自転車こいで　太陽をめがけて
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:36.25,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在泳池邊上 做了一個美夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:42.09,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你的聲音響起 讓我如痴如醉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:46.42,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}響徹耳畔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:51.26,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}昨天的我 宛如一隻幼貓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:56.94,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}隱約還記得 白色的皮毛顫抖著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:23:01.19,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}顫抖不已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:09.07,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}那是我墜入愛河的一天 是我愛上你的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:13.03,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}吶 請不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.03,0:23:20.04,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}墜入愛河的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:25.00,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}踏上自行車去看海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:28.88,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在拂曉的天空朝太陽奔去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.88,0:23:32.64,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不需修飾的日子裡繼續聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:40.23,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}踏上自行車奔向太陽
